%N A397079 Expansion of g.f. (Sum_{j>=1} x^j/(1-x^j))^2 * Product_{k>=1} 1/(1-x^k).
%F A397079 a(n) ~ sqrt(3) * exp(Pi*sqrt(2*n/3)) * (log(6*n/Pi^2) + 2*gamma)^2 / (8*Pi^2), where gamma is the Euler-Mascheroni constant A001620.
%t A397079 nmax = 50; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[x^j/(1-x^j), {j, 1, nmax}]^2 / Product[1-x^k, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]
